    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery out of corners. The chassis remains sharp with a well-sorted MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with precise throttle response and balanced weight distribution.",
