      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and refined style, perfect for a buyer seeking a dependable daily driver. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish with only minor, negligible signs of road use that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free, featuring well-preserved seating surfaces and a fully functional dashboard where every electronic component works flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced regularly, offering a smooth gear transition and a quiet, composed ride. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of worry-free driving.",
